                        <lb/>
                        <seg ana="#animauxSauvages">Brosses</seg> (1) et <seg ana="#animauxSauvages">corbeilles</seg> (2) dans lesquelles <seg ana="#animauxSauvages">l'abeille</seg> emmagasine <seg ana="#scienceNat">le pollen</seg>.
                     </caption>
